This paper deals with image segmentation using deep neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of semi-supervised learning, which is a subfield of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of medical images for segmentation also suggests the possibility of the paper being categorized under multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper discusses the use of autoencoding, which is a technique commonly used in neural networks (cs.NE).
